# FINE COIN - Telegram Tap-to-Earn Bot Implementation Plan

## 🏗 Architecture Overview

```
fine-coin/
├── server/
│   ├── index.js              # Express server + Telegram Bot setup
│   ├── database.js           # PostgreSQL connection & schema
│   ├── routes/
│   │   ├── game.js           # Tap, energy, balance APIs
│   │   ├── upgrades.js       # Upgrade purchase APIs
│   │   ├── stars.js          # Telegram Stars store APIs
│   │   ├── invite.js         # Referral system APIs
│   │   └── wallet.js         # Wallet APIs
│   ├── middleware/
│   │   ├── auth.js           # Telegram initData validation
│   │   └── antiCheat.js      # Rate limiting & anti-bot measures
│   └── utils/
│       └── telegram.js       # Telegram Bot API helpers
├── public/
│   ├── index.html            # Main SPA entry
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── style.css         # All styling
│   ├── js/
│   │   ├── app.js            # Main app controller
│   │   ├── game.js           # Tap game logic
│   │   ├── upgrades.js       # Upgrades UI
│   │   ├── store.js          # Stars store UI
│   │   ├── invite.js         # Invite/referral UI
│   │   ├── wallet.js         # Wallet UI
│   │   └── api.js            # API client
│   └── assets/
│       └── (generated images)
├── package.json
├── .env.example
└── README.md
```

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS + Telegram Mini Apps SDK
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express
- **Database**: PostgreSQL (via `pg` package)
- **Bot Framework**: `node-telegram-bot-api`
- **Theme**: "This is Fine" meme dog, fire effects, warm orange/amber palette

## 📱 Screens / Tabs
1. **PLAY** - Main tap area with fire dog, energy bar, balance, countdown
2. **UPGRADES** - Tap Power, Max Energy, Recharge Rate upgrades
3. **STARS STORE** - Telegram Stars unlimited energy packages
4. **INVITE** - Referral link, bonus info
5. **WALLET** - Wallet connection panel (locked until distribution)

## 🎮 Game Mechanics
- Base tap rate: 0.2 FINE per tap (5 taps = 1 FINE)
- Energy: 1000 max, 1 per tap, 10/min regen
- Upgrades increase tap power, max energy, regen rate
- Anti-cheat: server-side rate limiting, energy validation

## 💰 Monetization
- Telegram Stars for unlimited energy packages
- 30 min = 5 Stars, 1 hour = 8 Stars, 24 hours = 50 Stars

## 📅 Distribution
- 2-month countdown from launch
- FINE Coin balance determines memecoin distribution ratio
